OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPerhaps the odd early brighter
OL,6,Fspell in the east. However, cloud soon
OL,7,Fthickening ahead of rain spreading
OL,8,Feast during the morning, occasionally
OL,9,Fheavy. A few drier intervals are
OL,10,Fpossible through the afternoon, but
OL,11,Falso heavy showers. Breezy, and rather
OL,12,Fcool.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with showers
OL,15,Fcontinuing through the evening, before
OL,16,Flikely merging into more persistent
OL,17,Fand occasionally heavy rain. Rain
OL,18,Ferratically clearing east around dawn,
OL,19,Fbut with further showers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,168,160,301,260,100,100
